subject: DNL343 Study: New SAE Report - Site 101
body:
Dear Study Team,

Please find the attached CIOMS form for a Serious Adverse Event (unexpected hospitalization) for participant 101-005 in the DNL343 study.

Kindly acknowledge receipt at your earliest convenience and advise on any additional reporting requirements.

Best regards,

Dr. Emily Carter
Principal Investigator
University of Wisconsin

subject: Re: DNL343 Study: New SAE Report - Site 101
body:
Dear Dr. Carter,

Thank you for the notification. We have received the CIOMS form for participant 101-005.

The sponsor team will review the report and provide further guidance shortly.

Best,

Sarah Chen
Clinical Research Associate
Syneos Health
